1
00:00:05,005 --> 00:00:06,756
(stinging sound)

2
00:00:06,840 --> 00:00:07,674
(Toru) Ah...

3
00:00:07,757 --> 00:00:10,552
(Mari) Please wait! This person is important!

4
00:00:10,635 --> 00:00:12,470
(Akari) I will become the governor of Tokyo.

5
00:00:12,554 --> 00:00:14,889
‎I'll do my best so I can make it

6
00:00:14,973 --> 00:00:16,975
A world where you feel glad to be alive

7
00:00:17,058 --> 00:00:18,226
(Akari) I'm going to become the governor of Tokyo!

8
00:00:18,309 --> 00:00:19,144
(Announcer) Today morning

9
00:00:19,227 --> 00:00:21,813
At the pedestrian deck of Tachikawa Higashi

10
00:00:21,896 --> 00:00:23,398
Popular video streamer⸺

11
00:00:23,481 --> 00:00:25,567
Tohru from Bright Blind

12
00:00:25,650 --> 00:00:27,777
I was stabbed with a knife by a man I didn't know.

13
00:00:27,861 --> 00:00:28,945
taken to hospital

14
00:00:31,990 --> 00:00:33,533
I can't believe it...

15
00:00:33,616 --> 00:00:35,577
Even just splitting the party would be amazing.

16
00:00:35,660 --> 00:00:37,495
How could I pull out that Kazama Aoi?

17
00:00:37,579 --> 00:00:38,788
Did you know each other?

18
00:00:38,872 --> 00:00:41,332
(Hotaru) Regarding the introduction of AI in government during his time as mayor

19
00:00:41,416 --> 00:00:42,542
‎Consultation: Ask for a ride

20
00:00:44,127 --> 00:00:45,545
I mean, it's more than that.

21
00:00:49,549 --> 00:00:51,676
‎You only have one life, prioritize it!

22
00:00:54,345 --> 00:00:55,513
‎Promise

23
00:00:56,181 --> 00:00:57,390
‎-(Akari) Yes‎-(Mari) Yes

24
00:00:57,932 --> 00:00:59,350
‎What about the child who was bitten?

25
00:00:59,434 --> 00:01:01,811
He said he would be able to be discharged from the hospital in about 10 days.

26
00:01:01,895 --> 00:01:04,189
Haha, then you can leave that behind for now.

27
00:01:04,272 --> 00:01:07,066
I can't leave it behind, but please leave it behind.

28
00:01:11,946 --> 00:01:14,073
(Mari) I promise! This person is...

29
00:01:14,157 --> 00:01:16,075
(Akari) I'm going to become the governor of Tokyo!

30
00:01:16,159 --> 00:01:18,745
‎He has announced his candidacy. This

31
00:01:18,828 --> 00:01:19,662
‎Will that happen?

32
00:01:19,746 --> 00:01:22,832
(Mari) It is very regrettable that it is different from the original plan.

33
00:01:22,916 --> 00:01:24,417
Even for us, in response to an unexpected situation...

34
00:01:24,501 --> 00:01:25,877
‎I don't need that.

35
00:01:26,544 --> 00:01:28,213
(Mari/Akari) I'm sorry.

36
00:01:30,965 --> 00:01:32,509
Mr. Igarashi?

37
00:01:33,176 --> 00:01:34,803
(Akari) Are you angry?

38
00:01:34,886 --> 00:01:36,513
(Hotaru) Huh? Are you okay

39
00:01:36,596 --> 00:01:39,349
Currently updating to the latest version

40
00:01:40,350 --> 00:01:41,893
‎Yes Reboot

41
00:01:43,061 --> 00:01:47,315
♪～

42
00:02:41,953 --> 00:02:45,039
‎～♪

43
00:02:49,377 --> 00:02:51,838
(Fireflies) It's already started, isn't it?

44
00:02:51,921 --> 00:02:53,756
(Igarashi) Being searched by a bad guy

45
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:55,091
‎It's worse than being completely overtaken...

46
00:02:55,175 --> 00:02:56,467
(Mari) I made the first move.

47
00:02:56,551 --> 00:03:00,013
After this, Tooru will release an emergency video as part of the disclosure.

48
00:03:00,096 --> 00:03:00,972
‎Are you okay?

49
00:03:01,055 --> 00:03:02,891
‎You can do it if it's live streaming.

50
00:03:02,974 --> 00:03:04,726
‎(Hotaru) Sigh~ That's tough.

51
00:03:04,809 --> 00:03:07,270
(Mari) Originally, broadcasting from the hospital room was against the rules.

52
00:03:07,353 --> 00:03:08,980
Although it is painful,

53
00:03:09,063 --> 00:03:11,774
It's a private room, so I'd appreciate it if you wouldn't let me be identified.

54
00:03:11,858 --> 00:03:15,778
‎Okay, before the mass media hits you, create a hypothetical question and answer.

55
00:03:15,862 --> 00:03:19,115
‎Build and share stories for that purpose

56
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:20,033
‎Story?

57
00:03:20,116 --> 00:03:22,410
It's so flashy since he announced his candidacy.

58
00:03:22,493 --> 00:03:26,205
A story with persuasive power and centripetal force that supports and pulls it is necessary.

59
00:03:26,289 --> 00:03:28,583
‎There are some things you shouldn't talk about.

60
00:03:28,666 --> 00:03:30,710
(Mari) What you should definitely keep secret about the current situation

61
00:03:30,793 --> 00:03:33,004
‎I asked Tooru for buzz cooperation.

62
00:03:33,087 --> 00:03:34,964
‎That's something I'll take to my grave.

63
00:03:35,048 --> 00:03:35,882
(Firefly/Akari) Understood

64
00:03:35,965 --> 00:03:38,051
‎This is still the case with that letter.

65
00:03:38,134 --> 00:03:39,177
‎I understand

66
00:03:39,260 --> 00:03:43,473
(Igarashi) The reason for the daughter's resignation was because of her relationship with her father, the secretary general of the Democratic Party.

67
00:03:43,556 --> 00:03:45,934
‎When I was worried about differences in political views

68
00:03:46,017 --> 00:03:48,811
Akari was consulted about running for governor of Tokyo...

69
00:03:48,895 --> 00:03:52,190
‎Falled in love with her personality‎Determined to support her

70
00:03:52,273 --> 00:03:54,400
‎I left the Democratic Party due to reasons.

71
00:03:54,484 --> 00:03:57,946
(Akari) Ah... Should I just ask for advice?

72
00:03:58,029 --> 00:04:00,156
Sorry, but I want you to lie about that.

73
00:04:00,907 --> 00:04:02,951
(Mari) From a candidate who was pulled out by someone

74
00:04:03,034 --> 00:04:05,495
Candidates who stand up for themselves are better

75
00:04:05,578 --> 00:04:07,789
‎Because it earns the trust of voters.

76
00:04:09,874 --> 00:04:11,251
I did the same thing too

77
00:04:11,334 --> 00:04:12,335
‎Huh?

78
00:04:12,418 --> 00:04:14,504
(Hotaru) The truth is, until I was invited to Gala-san.

79
00:04:14,587 --> 00:04:17,548
I had never thought of running for mayor.

80
00:04:17,632 --> 00:04:22,136
‎That's a bit... ‎I'd say it's a lie.

81
00:04:22,220 --> 00:04:24,889
‎Change the order ‎Change your memory

82
00:04:24,973 --> 00:04:27,475
‎Change order and memory?

83
00:04:27,558 --> 00:04:28,393
‎Yeah

84
00:04:28,476 --> 00:04:31,729
‎I want to be mayor ‎At a soup kitchen

85
00:04:31,813 --> 00:04:34,190
I talked to Mr. Gala, who I knew by sight.

86
00:04:34,274 --> 00:04:37,527
Well, if you say it's a lie, that's it.

87
00:04:37,610 --> 00:04:41,656
It's not like I'm going to hurt anyone, and I'll be more prepared that way.

88
00:04:41,739 --> 00:04:44,033
‎I seriously want to believe that.

89
00:04:45,285 --> 00:04:48,413
If there seems to be some resistance...

90
00:04:48,496 --> 00:04:50,707
‎It's okay, I'll try it

91
00:04:51,499 --> 00:04:52,333
‎Thank you

92
00:04:53,001 --> 00:04:55,670
-(Hotaru) What about us? -(Igarashi) Should I still lie down?

93
00:04:55,753 --> 00:04:58,339
‎The matter of the lieutenant governor is useless. ‎Do not offend the assembly⸺

94
00:04:58,423 --> 00:05:00,258
‎I want to aim for how and when to put it out.

95
00:05:00,341 --> 00:05:03,886
(Mari) Originally, nominations require the consent of Congress.

96
00:05:03,970 --> 00:05:05,430
(Firefly) When to put it out?

97
00:05:05,513 --> 00:05:07,515
(Igarashi) May 21st

98
00:05:07,598 --> 00:05:11,769
‎We will hold a press conference on this day as planned‎And...

99
00:05:11,853 --> 00:05:13,771
‎(Mari) ‎Tell the crowd of reporters

100
00:05:13,855 --> 00:05:15,440
‎I'll tell you everything there.

101
00:05:15,523 --> 00:05:17,775
(Igarashi) Yes, you can buy time.

102
00:05:17,859 --> 00:05:20,820
An unknown newcomer held a press conference announcing his candidacy that was ignored by the media.

103
00:05:20,903 --> 00:05:22,739
‎You can pick it up even if you are interested.

104
00:05:22,822 --> 00:05:24,949
(Hotaru) Well, until then...

105
00:05:26,993 --> 00:05:28,411
‎I need to make this

106
00:05:32,582 --> 00:05:35,251
(Mari) To that end, we need to solidify our policies.

107
00:05:35,334 --> 00:05:38,338
At the press conference, Akari spoke about it in her own words.

108
00:05:38,421 --> 00:05:40,131
‎You need to feel it

109
00:05:41,507 --> 00:05:45,094
‎Desktop theory has the opposite effect.

110
00:05:45,178 --> 00:05:48,431
(Mari) We will create a place for dialogue with Tokyo residents from various positions.

111
00:05:48,514 --> 00:05:49,807
(Fireflies) I'll connect too

112
00:05:49,891 --> 00:05:52,477
People who have left the party or are raising children, etc.

113
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:54,854
- (Mari) That's helpful! - (Igarashi) Let's take a photo later.

114
00:05:54,937 --> 00:05:56,272
‎Let's do it together with the poster

115
00:05:56,355 --> 00:05:57,190
(Mari) I will make arrangements.

116
00:05:57,273 --> 00:05:59,901
‎However, there is no answer to that extent.

117
00:05:59,984 --> 00:06:02,070
‎Incite speculation or lose interest

118
00:06:02,153 --> 00:06:05,114
‎Relationship with the young lady Motivation for running for office

119
00:06:05,198 --> 00:06:07,325
It is better to answer these two questions in advance.

120
00:06:07,408 --> 00:06:08,785
‎The tataki is already made.

121
00:06:08,868 --> 00:06:09,911
‎When?

122
00:06:10,828 --> 00:06:13,956
(Mari) It was created to keep lies to a minimum.

123
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,750
-(Akari) Thank you‎-(Mari) No.

124
00:06:15,833 --> 00:06:18,669
I also don't want to lie as much as possible.

125
00:06:18,753 --> 00:06:21,464
‎Our encounter already has a strong narrative quality.

126
00:06:21,547 --> 00:06:24,967
I don't think it's necessary to elaborate, so I'll share the facts.

127
00:06:25,551 --> 00:06:30,306
‎Hoshino‎Mari is returning from a meeting with a certain company‎She loses her mother's keepsake amulet on the road at night

128
00:06:30,932 --> 00:06:32,850
-(Igarashi) That light bulb? -(Mari) Yes

129
00:06:32,934 --> 00:06:36,312
As I was desperately searching for Tsukioka Akari passed by.

130
00:06:36,396 --> 00:06:40,024
Even after I gave up, you stayed and searched for me...

131
00:06:40,108 --> 00:06:42,318
‎2 hours... no, 4 hours

132
00:06:42,401 --> 00:06:44,278
-(Akari/Mari) Huh?-(Igarashi) The time I searched.

133
00:06:44,362 --> 00:06:45,655
No, it took me about 20 minutes...

134
00:06:45,738 --> 00:06:47,365
(Sound of tapping on desk) (Igarashi) Story!

135
00:06:47,448 --> 00:06:48,783
‎Yeah

136
00:06:48,866 --> 00:06:51,661
(Mari) About 4 hours dripping sweat

137
00:06:52,370 --> 00:06:53,996
Please look for it while wiping it...

138
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:56,124
‎Ah... wait

139
00:06:56,207 --> 00:06:58,209
Will it drip? sweat

140
00:06:58,292 --> 00:06:59,252
It's 4 hours, right?

141
00:06:59,961 --> 00:07:00,837
‎It drips

142
00:07:02,672 --> 00:07:04,132
There was...

143
00:07:06,050 --> 00:07:07,385
‎Will it drip?

144
00:07:08,261 --> 00:07:09,929
‎At Snack Toshiko…

145
00:07:10,513 --> 00:07:12,014
“It was shining”

146
00:07:12,098 --> 00:07:14,434
I said that, but was it the timing?

147
00:07:14,517 --> 00:07:18,604
Illegal intrusion onto our rooftop should be kept a secret.

148
00:07:18,688 --> 00:07:19,939
‎This is a famous quote, so here it is.

149
00:07:19,939 --> 00:07:20,940
(Igarashi) Recruitment‎This is a great quote, so here it is.

150
00:07:21,023 --> 00:07:22,150
‎Thank you

151
00:07:22,233 --> 00:07:24,944
But if it was lit, wouldn't it take 4 hours?

152
00:07:26,446 --> 00:07:29,490
‎Next, about the motivation for running for office.

153
00:07:29,574 --> 00:07:33,035
‎Akari Tsukioka served as the mother ‎To Toshiko Snack

154
00:07:33,119 --> 00:07:37,165
‎People of all ages, men and women, from various positions and professions gather together.

155
00:07:37,248 --> 00:07:40,209
Heated political discussions were held every day.

156
00:07:40,293 --> 00:07:42,503
‎No, you lied all of a sudden.

157
00:07:42,587 --> 00:07:44,130
‎Sorry

158
00:07:44,213 --> 00:07:45,631
‎I will reconsider

159
00:07:45,715 --> 00:07:47,341
(Fireflies) Even if it's not a political discussion

160
00:07:47,425 --> 00:07:50,470
You've heard stories from many different people, haven't you?

161
00:07:50,553 --> 00:07:53,556
Akari-chan herself has experienced many things.

162
00:07:53,639 --> 00:07:58,436
‎Individual efforts won't do anything ‎Unreasonableness or difficulty in living

163
00:07:58,936 --> 00:08:01,272
‎Various walls and divisions

164
00:08:02,064 --> 00:08:05,860
(Mari) As I continue to meet and have dialogues with a wide variety of people,

165
00:08:05,943 --> 00:08:09,030
The pursuit of individual happiness and politics are inseparable

166
00:08:09,113 --> 00:08:12,700
‎Have a strong interest and start learning

167
00:08:13,743 --> 00:08:17,371
‎Is there anything I can do?

168
00:08:17,955 --> 00:08:19,373
‎I want to do something

169
00:08:19,457 --> 00:08:21,167
‎That kind of feeling grows every day

170
00:08:21,250 --> 00:08:23,502
While looking for a way

171
00:08:25,213 --> 00:08:26,964
‎Meet Mari Hoshino

172
00:08:28,257 --> 00:08:29,509
‎I see.

173
00:08:30,885 --> 00:08:33,262
‎Change the order

174
00:08:34,305 --> 00:08:36,432
‎Change memory

175
00:08:39,894 --> 00:08:41,062
But...

176
00:08:42,980 --> 00:08:45,608
There are some things you shouldn't change.

177
00:08:48,486 --> 00:08:52,156
There's something I need to talk to everyone about.

178
00:09:04,585 --> 00:09:05,503
(Ryusei) Hey Subaru

179
00:09:07,255 --> 00:09:08,464
(Subaru) Excuse me.

180
00:09:13,135 --> 00:09:14,553
‎Wow, that's amazing.

181
00:09:23,145 --> 00:09:24,146
‎Nursing teacher…

182
00:09:24,230 --> 00:09:25,565
‎I am a teacher in the health room.

183
00:09:25,648 --> 00:09:27,984
Yes, I understand, thank you

184
00:09:53,592 --> 00:09:56,137
(Light) This is me

185
00:10:01,684 --> 00:10:03,811
I'm really sorry

186
00:10:05,187 --> 00:10:06,981
‎Keep quiet about something important like this.

187
00:10:07,064 --> 00:10:11,235
‎No, he really wanted to talk to me.

188
00:10:14,071 --> 00:10:14,905
‎What happened?

189
00:10:25,499 --> 00:10:28,961
‎There was a student going to school in the health room.

190
00:10:29,754 --> 00:10:34,467
I didn't go to school for half a year from April of my second year.

191
00:10:34,550 --> 00:10:35,968
‎Thank you for coming so hard.

192
00:10:36,052 --> 00:10:37,928
‎Oh, it's an oyster

193
00:10:41,349 --> 00:10:42,683
‎Looks delicious

194
00:10:43,809 --> 00:10:46,228
‎Oh~ Jippuru

195
00:10:51,984 --> 00:10:54,445
(Akari) That's amazing

196
00:10:54,528 --> 00:10:57,823
This is what it looked like to this child

197
00:10:58,699 --> 00:11:02,912
Being able to turn that into reality is a great talent.

198
00:11:03,871 --> 00:11:07,333
I feel like I've found a treasure

199
00:11:07,917 --> 00:11:12,505
Having that kind of feeling for a student

200
00:11:13,631 --> 00:11:17,968
I should have been more careful.

201
00:11:19,553 --> 00:11:23,599
I heard that you were making it at home even when you weren't going to school.

202
00:11:23,682 --> 00:11:25,559
‎(Akari) Cute

203
00:11:26,310 --> 00:11:27,603
Mr. Suzuhara?

204
00:11:29,563 --> 00:11:34,068
Eh, maybe Kokoro Yamagishi, who transferred in March?

205
00:11:37,029 --> 00:11:39,865
‎We were good friends, the two of us were always together.

206
00:11:41,867 --> 00:11:44,161
‎Leave me someday

207
00:11:45,162 --> 00:11:47,873
Become seeds in each place

208
00:11:47,957 --> 00:11:52,837
Become a tree and bloom flowers

209
00:11:53,712 --> 00:11:55,548
‎Give fruit...

210
00:11:58,843 --> 00:12:01,011
But I wish we could have stuck together a little longer.

211
00:12:07,017 --> 00:12:08,644
‎Beautiful eyes

212
00:12:09,812 --> 00:12:11,105
‎Like a star

213
00:12:14,650 --> 00:12:16,527
‎Do you feel a little lonely?

214
00:12:18,779 --> 00:12:21,365
(Honoka) I want to disappear...

215
00:12:23,159 --> 00:12:23,993
‎Huh?

216
00:12:24,702 --> 00:12:28,873
(Honoka) Classroom When I'm alone

217
00:12:31,041 --> 00:12:32,543
Are you lonely?

218
00:12:33,502 --> 00:12:34,837
(Honoka) Also...

219
00:12:37,548 --> 00:12:39,425
‎I'm embarrassed

220
00:12:40,551 --> 00:12:42,261
I wish it would disappear

221
00:12:44,221 --> 00:12:47,683
I want to disappear, disappear...

222
00:12:49,101 --> 00:12:52,313
But I can't erase it

223
00:12:53,898 --> 00:12:55,232
(Akari) I see.

224
00:12:56,150 --> 00:12:58,694
This kid is keeping it at bay.

225
00:13:00,821 --> 00:13:04,200
‎Don't let Suzuhara-san disappear

226
00:13:13,375 --> 00:13:16,504
Thank you for not disappearing

227
00:13:20,382 --> 00:13:23,844
‎Teacher, I would like to see more of ‎Mr. Suzuhara's dolls.

228
00:13:27,640 --> 00:13:30,142
(Akari) Steps to return to the classroom

229
00:13:30,226 --> 00:13:32,144
At that time she

230
00:13:32,228 --> 00:13:36,690
‎2 hours a day of self-study at the health room

231
00:13:36,774 --> 00:13:40,861
Since it was just a simple task, I thought it was the best choice.

232
00:13:41,946 --> 00:13:46,158
Both my homeroom teacher and the principal agreed with me.

233
00:13:48,035 --> 00:13:50,621
(Light) Should I put it somewhere wider?

234
00:13:51,163 --> 00:13:53,082
‎Dries quickly

235
00:13:53,165 --> 00:13:56,418
Ah, I see. The weather is nice today.

236
00:13:57,169 --> 00:13:58,003
(Honoka) Yeah

237
00:14:02,341 --> 00:14:03,551
‎Maybe...

238
00:14:11,976 --> 00:14:13,561
(Honoka) Sensei's child?

239
00:14:13,644 --> 00:14:16,438
(Akari) Yes, I went to the sky a long time ago.

240
00:14:16,522 --> 00:14:18,148
‎Aren't you going to keep it again?

241
00:14:18,983 --> 00:14:23,112
It's sad to say goodbye, but it's no good in my current apartment.

242
00:14:23,195 --> 00:14:25,531
‎Chaton Sakurada town

243
00:14:26,532 --> 00:14:27,783
‎Chaton?

244
00:14:28,742 --> 00:14:30,911
‎Kitten in French

245
00:14:34,999 --> 00:14:38,544
(Honoka) We can live together in Chaton and Sakurada Town.

246
00:14:44,341 --> 00:14:45,467
‎Thank you

247
00:14:46,677 --> 00:14:50,723
(Akari) I thought I was giving proper guidance.

248
00:14:50,806 --> 00:14:53,809
(Saya) Please don't let my daughter make dolls.

249
00:14:53,893 --> 00:14:55,686
‎What is that...

250
00:14:55,769 --> 00:14:58,981
(Saya) After I stopped going to school, where did I learn it?

251
00:14:59,064 --> 00:15:02,359
‎Buy the ingredients at 100 yen store and start making it.

252
00:15:02,443 --> 00:15:06,447
‎I stopped studying and helping around the house ‎My days and nights were reversed.

253
00:15:06,530 --> 00:15:09,950
That's why I banned making dolls at my house.

254
00:15:10,034 --> 00:15:11,744
After I was able to go to school properly

255
00:15:12,328 --> 00:15:16,707
Suzuhara-san, you work hard every day.

256
00:15:17,499 --> 00:15:20,169
It doesn't mean you're keeping your promise to your mother...

257
00:15:20,252 --> 00:15:22,838
‎Two hours in the nurse's office‎Just doing what you like.

258
00:15:22,922 --> 00:15:26,508
(Homeroom teacher) Even going to school at the school nurse's office will be treated as attendance.

259
00:15:26,592 --> 00:15:29,553
(Saya) But it will be written in the report.

260
00:15:29,637 --> 00:15:31,889
‎“Difficulty working in groups”

261
00:15:31,972 --> 00:15:32,932
‎That's...

262
00:15:33,015 --> 00:15:35,517
‎Group action is not everything

263
00:15:35,601 --> 00:15:40,064
Mr. Suzuhara talked a lot and laughed at the nurse's office...

264
00:15:40,147 --> 00:15:44,610
(Saya) I'm in trouble, even if I can only talk to people who pamper me.

265
00:15:45,235 --> 00:15:47,947
You say it's not everything.

266
00:15:48,030 --> 00:15:51,617
How many jobs are there that you can get even if you can't work in a group?

267
00:15:51,700 --> 00:15:53,952
‎Before that, it will affect the entrance exam.

268
00:15:54,036 --> 00:15:56,163
If you don't take classes, your grades will be evaluated...

269
00:15:56,246 --> 00:16:00,084
(Akari) Regular tests can also be taken at the health room.

270
00:16:01,043 --> 00:16:02,961
If you study hard at home...

271
00:16:03,045 --> 00:16:05,130
(Saya) I'm the one who's going to make you do that, right?

272
00:16:06,882 --> 00:16:08,133
‎Sorry

273
00:16:08,717 --> 00:16:11,095
I'll do it, of course I'm a parent.

274
00:16:12,054 --> 00:16:14,014
I can't leave you alone during the day.

275
00:16:14,098 --> 00:16:15,599
I also quit my job

276
00:16:15,683 --> 00:16:18,811
But my daughter told me

277
00:16:18,894 --> 00:16:21,188
‎My teacher doesn't tell me to study.

278
00:16:21,271 --> 00:16:24,358
She says she loves my doll

279
00:16:24,984 --> 00:16:29,363
In the future, I will become a doll maker, so I don't need to study at school.

280
00:16:30,072 --> 00:16:33,951
If the teachers just let them graduate, that would be the end of it.

281
00:16:34,034 --> 00:16:36,995
‎You don't have to force yourself to come to school. ‎You say it's ok to run away.

282
00:16:37,079 --> 00:16:39,039
‎I'm just saying it simply.

283
00:16:39,123 --> 00:16:43,585
‎Thus, possibilities and options‎are disappearing more and more.

284
00:16:43,669 --> 00:16:46,422
The one who will suffer in the future is that child herself.

285
00:16:47,005 --> 00:16:49,758
‎Parents are the ones who take care of that.

286
00:16:53,679 --> 00:16:57,891
I'm sorry for not being considerate enough.

287
00:17:01,395 --> 00:17:02,438
‎Just

288
00:17:03,230 --> 00:17:05,691
I don't think that once I graduate, that's the end...

289
00:17:05,774 --> 00:17:10,529
‎Switching to instruction other than doll making‎We aim to return to the classroom as soon as possible.

290
00:17:13,365 --> 00:17:16,118
(Homeroom teacher) Please stop making irresponsible comments.

291
00:17:16,201 --> 00:17:17,286
It's impossible

292
00:17:17,369 --> 00:17:21,248
How can a teacher be responsible for one student's life?

293
00:17:22,416 --> 00:17:23,625
(Teacher) It's definitely good.

294
00:17:23,709 --> 00:17:25,669
‎Personally, I love it

295
00:17:25,753 --> 00:17:28,547
‎I wonder if I can exhibit it at the city art exhibition?

296
00:17:29,131 --> 00:17:30,090
‎Why?

297
00:17:31,133 --> 00:17:34,595
The challenge is to make food that looks exactly like it.

298
00:17:35,179 --> 00:17:36,930
‎If you recommend this

299
00:17:37,014 --> 00:17:40,058
‎Assignment: I feel sorry for the children I protected and created.

300
00:17:47,441 --> 00:17:49,193
(Akari) Suzuhara-san?

301
00:17:51,653 --> 00:17:52,488
(Honoka) Teacher...

302
00:17:52,571 --> 00:17:54,823
‎What happened?

303
00:17:54,907 --> 00:17:57,284
‎Don't make dolls

304
00:17:58,827 --> 00:17:59,661
‎My mother...

305
00:17:59,745 --> 00:18:01,163
‎I see.

306
00:18:04,458 --> 00:18:07,002
Did you tell anyone at home about coming here?

307
00:18:09,087 --> 00:18:10,422
‎Wait a minute

308
00:18:11,131 --> 00:18:13,967
(Honoka) Oh no, don't say that.

309
00:18:14,802 --> 00:18:16,929
I'm worried about my family

310
00:18:18,055 --> 00:18:21,975
‎Teacher, I'll send it to you. Let's go home today.

311
00:18:22,059 --> 00:18:24,228
Right? Let's talk tomorrow at the nurse's office.

312
00:18:24,311 --> 00:18:27,731
'Cause I don't have to go anymore. Infirmary.

313
00:18:27,815 --> 00:18:30,609
‎-(Akari) Eh... ‎-(Honoka) Teacher, don't you know?

314
00:18:30,692 --> 00:18:32,903
Did your mother just say that?

315
00:18:36,448 --> 00:18:39,535
(Akari) Hey Suzuhara-san, wait.

316
00:18:39,618 --> 00:18:42,746
(Akari) Wait! Hey, wait a minute.

317
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:43,997
‎Wait!

318
00:18:44,832 --> 00:18:46,458
- (Honoka) I say I'm going to die! -(Akari) Huh?

319
00:18:46,542 --> 00:18:49,545
‎(Honoka) ‎I told my mother that I was going to die!

320
00:18:49,628 --> 00:18:53,841
If you don't let me make a doll, I'll die if I can't go to the infirmary!

321
00:18:53,924 --> 00:18:57,427
‎No! ‎Hey, no, no!

322
00:18:57,511 --> 00:19:01,181
Hey, the word "death" is used for that kind of thing.

323
00:19:01,265 --> 00:19:04,977
If you use it for a transaction, you won't be able to get it back.

324
00:19:05,686 --> 00:19:08,981
Even if it goes well, even if it doesn't, it's painful

325
00:19:09,064 --> 00:19:12,651
Someday, I'll really have no choice but to die.

326
00:19:15,362 --> 00:19:17,030
‎Mr. Suzuhara

327
00:19:17,114 --> 00:19:18,782
‎Somehow...

328
00:19:20,617 --> 00:19:22,619
‎Let's somehow reach adulthood

329
00:19:22,703 --> 00:19:24,246
‎If you do that...

330
00:19:24,329 --> 00:19:26,915
‎Now is not the time to become an adult.

331
00:19:29,251 --> 00:19:30,711
‎Now...

332
00:19:34,715 --> 00:19:36,133
I want to make it now

333
00:19:37,676 --> 00:19:39,303
‎Mr. Suzuhara...

334
00:19:43,515 --> 00:19:46,393
(Akari) I made a mistake here.

335
00:19:47,144 --> 00:19:50,564
‎Classroom Why not try your best?

336
00:19:51,773 --> 00:19:54,026
‎The teacher goes with me in the morning.

337
00:19:54,651 --> 00:19:58,071
If you have a hard time, come to the nurse's office during break time.

338
00:19:58,989 --> 00:20:03,160
I will tell the homeroom teacher and mother first.

339
00:20:10,918 --> 00:20:12,878
‎Speak for yourself

340
00:20:18,425 --> 00:20:21,053
‎Mr. Suzuhara, hey...

341
00:20:21,595 --> 00:20:26,808
(Akari) That night, I got a call from my homeroom teacher.

342
00:20:26,892 --> 00:20:28,977
‎Mr. Suzuhara

343
00:20:29,728 --> 00:20:32,064
‎I got into an argument with my mom.

344
00:20:33,732 --> 00:20:36,360
‎I jumped off the balcony

345
00:20:40,155 --> 00:20:43,825
It wasn't a deal, it was a bet.

346
00:20:46,078 --> 00:20:49,915
I didn't even know that

347
00:20:52,084 --> 00:20:54,544
What I was taught

348
00:20:56,421 --> 00:20:59,049
There were no life-threatening injuries.

349
00:21:00,384 --> 00:21:05,973
My responsibility was questioned and I was suspended from work.

350
00:21:08,850 --> 00:21:13,814
All contact with Mr. Suzuhara is prohibited.

351
00:21:18,360 --> 00:21:21,154
‎This photo was taken without permission

352
00:21:23,490 --> 00:21:25,450
‎Posted on SNS

353
00:21:26,118 --> 00:21:28,287
‎I cornered you

354
00:21:30,622 --> 00:21:33,041
I think it may have been a sexual relationship

355
00:21:35,127 --> 00:21:37,921
‎Don't hurt that girl any more⸺

356
00:21:38,005 --> 00:21:40,090
‎Management of SNS etc.

357
00:21:40,173 --> 00:21:42,968
I protested against news sites, etc., but I couldn't stop them.

358
00:21:44,469 --> 00:21:48,181
‎I can't be at school or home anymore

359
00:21:50,142 --> 00:21:52,352
Then I finally understood

360
00:21:53,687 --> 00:21:55,314
‎That girl said⸺

361
00:21:56,481 --> 00:21:58,483
I wish it would disappear

362
00:21:58,567 --> 00:22:01,319
I want to disappear, disappear

363
00:22:02,320 --> 00:22:04,031
But it can't disappear

364
00:22:06,450 --> 00:22:07,826
Disappear...

365
00:22:09,619 --> 00:22:11,538
It's okay now

366
00:22:12,456 --> 00:22:13,540
‎Understood

367
00:22:16,668 --> 00:22:20,630
Thank you very much for not disappearing

368
00:22:22,424 --> 00:22:23,800
‎That girl too...

369
00:22:27,054 --> 00:22:31,433
I hope that child doesn't disappear...

370
00:22:34,019 --> 00:22:37,647
‎Let's believe her 10 years

371
00:22:47,908 --> 00:22:50,410
‎Sorry thank you

372
00:22:52,454 --> 00:22:57,876
Her mother's feelings might be a little different now.

373
00:22:57,959 --> 00:22:59,377
‎Unlike 10 years ago

374
00:22:59,461 --> 00:23:02,672
‎Art and practical skills are also included in the report points.

375
00:23:02,756 --> 00:23:04,424
There are also online classes

376
00:23:04,966 --> 00:23:08,720
‎Remote work options are increasing in the future as well.

377
00:23:10,472 --> 00:23:13,183
We need a bigger invention

378
00:23:13,266 --> 00:23:17,062
‎Without burden on not only children but also teachers and parents

379
00:23:17,145 --> 00:23:20,357
A system that allows you to learn what you need according to your characteristics and circumstances

380
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:23,193
Child suicide rates continue to increase

381
00:23:24,111 --> 00:23:25,779
‎We absolutely have to stop it

382
00:23:26,404 --> 00:23:28,740
‎It's no good to stop it. ‎Reduce it to zero.

383
00:23:30,951 --> 00:23:33,662
‎Akari-san's case‎Will you take any measures?

384
00:23:33,745 --> 00:23:36,331
‎No, it's fine.

385
00:23:36,414 --> 00:23:37,624
‎No Guard Strategy

386
00:23:37,707 --> 00:23:40,127
-(Mari) Huh? -(Hotaru) What do you mean?

387
00:23:40,210 --> 00:23:42,963
(Igarashi) I believe in you for 10 years.

388
00:23:52,389 --> 00:23:54,724
(Igarashi) Okay, hypothetical questions and answers

389
00:23:55,225 --> 00:23:57,477
(Hotaru) Okay, okay?

390
00:23:58,854 --> 00:24:00,355
(Mari) Ah!

391
00:24:00,439 --> 00:24:03,442
The registered name here is Mr. Igarashi, right?

392
00:24:03,525 --> 00:24:05,318
‎If this is identified by the media

393
00:24:05,402 --> 00:24:07,863
There is a possibility that Mr. Igarashi's existence will suddenly become known...

394
00:24:07,946 --> 00:24:10,115
‎I want to avoid it suddenly.

395
00:24:10,198 --> 00:24:12,117
‎Would you like to be directed to another location?

396
00:24:12,200 --> 00:24:13,451
(Fireflies) How?

397
00:24:13,535 --> 00:24:17,622
(Sound of knocking on the door)

398
00:24:18,790 --> 00:24:23,795
(Sound of knocking on the door)

399
00:24:31,011 --> 00:24:32,387
(Mari) Amemiya-san!

400
00:24:32,971 --> 00:24:35,640
(Amemiya) Mari!

401
00:24:36,766 --> 00:24:39,478
‎Yes... Sorry for waiting‎Stung news

402
00:24:39,561 --> 00:24:43,857
‎That's what you see in the picture‎I'm sure it's Mari...

403
00:24:43,940 --> 00:24:47,277
‎Ah, that's good...

404
00:24:47,360 --> 00:24:49,279
‎Thank you for your concern.

405
00:24:52,324 --> 00:24:53,658
‎Mr. Amemiya

406
00:24:54,618 --> 00:24:55,660
‎What I would like to ask you...

407
00:24:55,744 --> 00:24:57,537
- (Amemiya) I'm happy - (Mari) Oh...

408
00:25:01,833 --> 00:25:05,837
(Toru) Well, as expected, this time was crazy.

409
00:25:06,588 --> 00:25:09,591
Somehow I'm still alive

410
00:25:09,674 --> 00:25:14,095
So, these two mysterious people?

411
00:25:16,264 --> 00:25:20,268
‎Identified identity

412
00:25:22,145 --> 00:25:23,188
‎Ah...

413
00:25:23,730 --> 00:25:27,526
This is what was dangerous

414
00:25:28,485 --> 00:25:30,987
‎For those who are not “wanting to become Tokyo governor”

415
00:25:31,071 --> 00:25:33,448
‎My father...

416
00:25:33,531 --> 00:25:36,076
(Reporters) Secretary-General Hoshino! ‎Secretary-chief! Secretary-General!

417
00:25:36,159 --> 00:25:39,120
(Reporter) Has Toren Chairman Kuzumaki's resignation from the party been accepted?

418
00:25:39,204 --> 00:25:41,831
The (Takaomi) Party is carefully considering the matter.

419
00:25:41,915 --> 00:25:43,917
(Reporter) What about Aio Kazama's endorsement?

420
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,710
(Takaomi) I have no involvement whatsoever.

421
00:25:45,794 --> 00:25:48,088
(Reporter) There are rumors that a young lady was involved in a street crime.

422
00:25:48,171 --> 00:25:49,422
(Takaomi) We have not received any reports.

423
00:25:49,506 --> 00:25:50,715
(Reporter) A woman who seemed to be accompanying her

424
00:25:50,799 --> 00:25:53,009
What about the fact that you announced your candidacy for Tokyo governor on the spot?

425
00:25:53,093 --> 00:25:54,427
(Takaomi) I have no involvement whatsoever.

426
00:25:54,511 --> 00:25:56,721
(Reporters) Hey, Secretary-General! ‎Secretary-chief! Secretary-General!

427
00:25:57,764 --> 00:26:01,518
(Amemiya) Huh? Did you find out where Mari Hoshino is?

428
00:26:01,601 --> 00:26:03,311
I'll be heading over right away

429
00:26:06,898 --> 00:26:08,149
(Reporter) Mari Hoshino!

430
00:26:08,233 --> 00:26:10,402
‎-(Mari) What about your business... ‎-(Reporter) Regarding the magical incident yesterday⸺

431
00:26:10,485 --> 00:26:13,280
Regarding your announcement of candidacy, could you tell us a little bit about it?

432
00:26:13,363 --> 00:26:15,699
(Reporter) What kind of relationship do you two have?

433
00:26:15,782 --> 00:26:16,825
(Mari) I'm a friend.

434
00:26:16,908 --> 00:26:18,910
(Reporter) Your friend's gubernatorial election

435
00:26:18,994 --> 00:26:20,704
Does that mean that Mari will support you?

436
00:26:20,787 --> 00:26:21,621
‎That's...

437
00:26:21,705 --> 00:26:23,498
(Reporter) What do you think about this matter?

438
00:26:23,582 --> 00:26:25,000
(Mari) My father has nothing to do with it.

439
00:26:25,083 --> 00:26:26,918
(Akari) Mari! ‎This is me

440
00:26:27,002 --> 00:26:27,836
‎Akari-san?

441
00:26:27,919 --> 00:26:29,921
‎Yes, nice to meet you!

442
00:26:30,005 --> 00:26:33,258
‎Akari Tsukioka‎My name is Akari Tsukioka.

443
00:26:33,341 --> 00:26:34,593
- (Reporter) Akari Tsukioka - (Akari) Yes.

444
00:26:34,676 --> 00:26:37,596
(Reporter) Is it correct to think of this as an announcement of your candidacy for the Tokyo gubernatorial election?

445
00:26:48,023 --> 00:26:50,150
(Akari) Thank you for joining us today.

446
00:26:53,236 --> 00:26:54,321
‎Although quickly

447
00:26:54,404 --> 00:26:57,032
If you have any problems, please let me know.

448
00:26:57,115 --> 00:26:58,908
(Parent) Some children have stopped attending school.

449
00:26:58,992 --> 00:27:01,286
(Parent) There is also the option of free school.

450
00:27:01,369 --> 00:27:03,038
‎The financial burden is heavy

451
00:27:03,121 --> 00:27:05,832
(Parent) I'm worried about my child locking the door and going out alone.

452
00:27:05,915 --> 00:27:07,250
(Nursery teacher) All I do is play with the kids.

453
00:27:07,334 --> 00:27:08,418
I tend to think that

454
00:27:08,501 --> 00:27:11,421
I'm told that I can't work overtime on the surface.

455
00:27:11,504 --> 00:27:14,758
(Female) There is daycare for sick children, but I can't make reservations at all.

456
00:27:14,841 --> 00:27:17,427
It's like going on the first train and returning on the last train.

457
00:27:22,265 --> 00:27:23,266
-(Firefly) I'll get it here.-(Light) Yes.

458
00:27:23,350 --> 00:27:25,477
‎Hey, waiting list for after-school children?

459
00:27:25,560 --> 00:27:27,145
-(Akari) How long have you been there? -(Mari) I'll look into it right away.

460
00:27:27,228 --> 00:27:29,939
(Igarashi) In addition, there are a certain number of problems with drunk customers and unauthorized cancellations.

461
00:27:30,023 --> 00:27:31,483
It's a mental burden

462
00:27:31,566 --> 00:27:32,984
-(Igarashi) What should I do? -(Hotaru) What should I do?

463
00:27:33,068 --> 00:27:34,277
(Akari/Mari) Deaf interpreter?

464
00:27:34,361 --> 00:27:38,740
First, I converted the audio into sign language.

465
00:27:38,823 --> 00:27:41,451
Ah, it's called a feeder. Give it to Maru-san.

466
00:27:41,534 --> 00:27:45,580
‎Easier to communicate to deaf people‎Convert to native sign language

467
00:27:45,663 --> 00:27:49,501
‎It rained a lot yesterday.

468
00:27:49,584 --> 00:27:51,461
‎It's sunny today

469
00:27:56,508 --> 00:27:58,426
(Akari/Mari) Ah~

470
00:27:58,510 --> 00:27:59,678
(Light) In everyday life

471
00:27:59,761 --> 00:28:02,013
If you have any trouble

472
00:28:02,097 --> 00:28:03,682
please tell me

473
00:28:05,183 --> 00:28:07,811
(Interpreter) When you suddenly collapse in your room.

474
00:28:07,894 --> 00:28:10,230
‎Contact emergency authorities...

475
00:28:10,313 --> 00:28:12,357
Yes, for example, GPS

476
00:28:12,440 --> 00:28:13,775
(Male) Ticket vending machines also have touch input.

477
00:28:13,858 --> 00:28:15,235
There were many

478
00:28:15,318 --> 00:28:18,571
(Male) Dogs that are not treated as assistance dogs will not be allowed in.

479
00:28:18,655 --> 00:28:21,991
What are guide dogs for?

480
00:28:22,075 --> 00:28:23,952
I was relieved when I heard it...

481
00:28:24,035 --> 00:28:25,412
(Male) When you get older

482
00:28:25,495 --> 00:28:27,747
There are still some people who find it difficult to commute.

483
00:28:27,831 --> 00:28:31,334
‎Shuttle service and such services‎I hope the city will consider this.

484
00:28:31,418 --> 00:28:33,211
‎I wonder if everyone can come here as a place to stay...

485
00:28:33,294 --> 00:28:35,588
Are you suffering from a sudden illness or injury?

486
00:28:35,672 --> 00:28:39,134
(Male) There is a shortage of doctors at the island's hospitals, so it is no longer possible to give birth.

487
00:28:39,217 --> 00:28:41,886
Even if there are young people who want to live on an island

488
00:28:41,970 --> 00:28:45,140
It's difficult if you're unsure about your childbirth and childcare arrangements.

489
00:28:45,223 --> 00:28:46,850
(Facility manager) Nursing care work

490
00:28:46,933 --> 00:28:49,644
It's more complicated and harder than before.

491
00:28:49,728 --> 00:28:52,188
Labor shortage is a chronic problem

492
00:28:52,272 --> 00:28:53,857
(Caregiver) It's not just a question of salary.

493
00:28:53,940 --> 00:28:56,443
‎The workplace remains the same after all.

494
00:28:59,404 --> 00:29:01,364
I want to decide on the axis of policy.

495
00:29:01,448 --> 00:29:03,658
(Akari) Living with anxiety

496
00:29:03,741 --> 00:29:05,869
It was impressive to hear him say something like that.

497
